import { CardGroup, Card } from "react-bootstrap"

function CarsCard({ cars }) {
    return (
        <>
            <CardGroup>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Title>{cars.BRAND} {cars.MODEL}</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src={cars.IMAGEM} alt='img' />
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Text>
                            Mileage between {cars.MIN_MILEAGE}km and {cars.MAX_MILEAGE}km
                        </Card.Text>
                        <Card.Text>
                            Dealer: {cars.DEALER}
                        </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Title>{cars.BRAND} {cars.MODEL}</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src={cars.IMAGEM} alt='img' />
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Text>
                            Mileage between {cars.MIN_MILEAGE}km and {cars.MAX_MILEAGE}km
                        </Card.Text>
                        <Card.Text>
                            Dealer: {cars.DEALER}
                        </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Title>{cars.BRAND} {cars.MODEL}</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src={cars.IMAGEM} alt='img' />
                    <Card.Body>
                        <Card.Text>
                            Mileage between {cars.MIN_MILEAGE}km and {cars.MAX_MILEAGE}km
                        </Card.Text>
                        <Card.Text>
                            Dealer: {cars.DEALER}
                        </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                </Card>
            </CardGroup>
        </>
    )
}

export default CarsCard;
